appspec.yml – CodeDeploy deployment configuration

pom.xml – Maven project configuration

How it was built

CI/CD pipeline configured using AWS CodePipeline

Build stage defined with CodeBuild and Maven

Deployment automated using CodeDeploy lifecycle hooks

Application tested by triggering deployments via GitHub commits

